Enums/LogLevel.html#/c:@M@APLogger@E@Log.abstract: Info log level. You may use this level on development to see some informative logs.

Enums/LogLevel.html#/c:@M@APLogger@E@Log.abstract: Warning log level. You may use this level to log some unexpected situations.

Enums/LogLevel.html#/c:@M@APLogger@E@Log.abstract: Error log level. You may use this level to log some unexpected situations which causes the code does not work correctly.

Enums/LogLevel.html#/c:@M@APLogger@E@Log.abstract: Fatal log level. You may use this level to log a serious situation. This situation may causes crash. Hope you won’t see this log.
